my first post:)

    My class started last June 6, 2007... how's my first wk.? bummer.  in my school every 3rd yr. we reshuffle, and i hate it. but look at the brighter side, you've got to meet new friends and enjoy new sets of activities. well, that's what i think.

    its like opening a new door towards reality[no sense at all] well, this is reality... and we have to face it. but then, i enjoy my class:) thanks to my new classmates.

    i realize a lot of things last summer... let me enumerate it for you..

1. Being a teenager  is fun! ----> its because you can enjoy  every activities without noticing the time.

2. more friends, much better---> this is the  most boring summer for me but because of my old friends and new friends... they help me get through with it.. *laugh*

3. being a geek...being cool!---> i read a lot of books this summer and i realize one thing. I LEARN A LOT!

4. summer jobs are in!---> its cool to have lots and lots of money... how? by asking your parents for it? nu-uh! you should at least try earning it! believe me.. its fun!

5. PHILIPPINES is a better place to live in---> boracay, palawan, cebu,bohol, tagaytay, baguio, METRO MANILA and a lot more.. no need for explanation...

    make sure you learn from everything you do. make sure you show love to all the people you knew.. cause you never know when or how will your life end....

    my point is... LOVE YOUR LIFE!

period.
